{
  "stem": "2533.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we stayed there until the 22nd of October, '42.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But before that, they burned down the-- the synagogue before we got to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, it would've been outside of the ghetto, not far from the police station on the main road.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They did-- they did it in only private houses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they knew that the rabbi was there, and then they knew when it was Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was the first raid that they took a lot of men away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was when the synagogue was-- was burned down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we used the people--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, that was-- yeah, when Yom Kippur or-- or Rosh Hashanah [INAUDIBLE] and that the Germans knew--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--when they were all-- all together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then in '42, we were already in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every morning, the same sort of work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was so hard during the winter because when the soil was frozen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And not even during the summer when I just got my portion of digging it, it was clay.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't easy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If I got sand, it was all right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sometimes there were lots of rocks, and the boys used to help-- help out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was sense, because there was a very nice, big river was running.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the river didn't run straight, only with a lot of curves and a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they wanted that river so the-- a lot of them [? pastures ?] There's a lot of the-- the-- want it to dry out, so there would be more length for the farmers or maybe a lot of the-- the Germans, they were taking everything over and just to make our life misery, and that-- that's what we went to work for.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
